                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/guardian/3_infinite1_015_033",
                                            "text": "%JamesHudson%: According to Department H, it's every bit as devious and cunning as the man it's patterned after.",
